\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Die <code><strong>Node.nodeValue</strong></code> Eigenschaft gibt den Wert der aktuellen Node zurück oder setzt ihn.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>value</var> = <var>node</var>.nodeValue;\n</pre>\n\n<p><code>value</code> ist ein string der den Inhalt, falls es ihn gibt, der aktuellen node enthält.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notizen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Für das Dokument selbst, gibt <code>nodeValue</code>&nbsp; <code>null</code> zurück. Für Text, Kommentar, und CDATA nodes, gibt <code>nodeValue</code> den Inhalt der node zurück. Für attribute nodes, wird der Inhalt des Attributes zurückgegeben.</p>\n\n<p>Die folgende Tabelle zeigt die return Werte der unterschiedlichen Elemente:</p>\n\n<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Attr</th>\n   <th>value of attribute</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>CDATASection</td>\n   <td>Inhalt der CDATA Section</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Comment</td>\n   <td>Inhalt des comments</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Document</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>DocumentFragment</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>DocumentType</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Element</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>NamedNodeMap</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>EntityReference</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Notation</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>ProcessingInstruction</td>\n   <td>Gesamter Inhalt, ausgenommen des target</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Text</td>\n   <td>Inhalt der text node</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Wenn <code>nodeValue</code> als <code>null</code> definiert wird, hat das null setzen keine Auswirkung.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-F68D080\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: Node.nodeValue</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Notizen","id":"notes"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"specification"}],"summary":"Die Node.nodeValue Eigenschaft gibt den Wert der aktuellen Node zurück oder setzt ihn.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.nodeValue","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/nodevalue","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/nodevalue/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue","title":"Node.nodeValue"}],"pageTitle":"Node.nodeValue - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}